    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      78.02,
      350.79,
      527.18,
      364.79
    ],
    "text": "The Counsel for the Appellant takes up the position that the case against the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      78.02,
      371.91,
      527.28,
      385.91
    ],
    "text": "Appellant should have been considered under the plea of sudden fight and",
