      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      99.38,
      476.45,
      527.08,
      490.45
    ],
    "text": "\u201cCulpable homicide is not murder if it is committed without",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      99.38,
      497.57,
      527.04,
      511.57
    ],
    "text": "premeditation in a sudden fight in the heat of passion upon a sudden",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      99.38,
      518.69,
      527.18,
      532.69
    ],
    "text": "quarrel, and without the offender having taken undue advantage or acted",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      99.38,
      539.93,
      297.43,
      553.93
    ],
